==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tactual
<hw>Tac"tu*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Tact</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the
sense, or the organs, of touch; derived from touch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In the lowest organisms we have a kind of <qex>tactual</qex> sense
diffused over the entire body.</q> <rj><qau>Tyndall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tadpole</ent>⟦br⟧
